high_descs: Turn right and walk to the fridge on the left.
Pick up the spoon on the top shelf of the fridge.
Turn around to walk into the kitchen to reach the cup next to the stove.
Put the spoon in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around to walk to the larger sink at the end of the counter.
Put the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Spoon with the Cup in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn and go to the fridge.
Take this spoon out of the refrigerator.
Go to the cooktop.
Put the phone in the empty cup.
Pick up the empty cup and spoon.
Turn and go to the far edge of the sink.
Put the cup and spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Spoon and Cup in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn right and move left in kitchen, then go along the fridge counter.
Head to the cupboard and pick up the spoon by opening the cupboard.
After closing the cup turn left and move near the stove which is on the kitchen counter.
Put the spoon in the cup which is near the stove.
Now pick the cup with spoon and turn left.
Then head to the sink.
Place the cup with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the spoon and cup in the SinkBasin.
